org.pipservices.commons.refer

Class Reference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pipservices.commons.refer.Reference

  • public class Reference
extends Object
    Contains a reference to a component and locator to find it. It is used by References to store registered component references.

      • match

        public boolean match(Object locator)
        Matches locator to this reference locator. Descriptors are matched using equal method. All other locator types are matched using direct comparison.
        Parameters:
        locator - the locator to match.
        Returns:
        true if locators are matching and false it they don't.
